nergy,\npositron density and positron temperature on these kinds of solitons are the\nsame as that for large amplitude IASWs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Feb 2011 18:08:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-04-12"}
