 numerically solving a large system of coupled differential equations, the\nproposed method is much simpler and more accurate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Feb 2011 23:37:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Jun 2011 15:49:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-06-02"}
