er-polynomial separation between the deterministic communication\ncomplexity and the logarithm of the rank of the communication tensor. This\nmeans that the log-rank conjecture does not hold in high dimensions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Feb 2011 00:07:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 19 Nov 2011 05:55:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-11-22"}
