ears have very likely not been correctly evaluated, and\nthat (2) the TSI variations over cycle 23 and the change in the TSI levels\nbetween the minima in 1996 and 2008 are consistent with the solar surface\nmagnetism mechanism.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Feb 2011 14:06:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-27"}
